<verse style="v" number="25" />Through the-same I-am-saying to{you} do_not_be-worrying to{the life} of{you}, what you-may-eat or what you-may-drink, nor to{the body} of{you}, what you-may-clothe-selves. The life is_emphatically-not_being more-than of{the nourishment} and the body of{the clothing}.
