<verse style="v" number="27" />Moreover, come[ing]-toward, the slaves of{the house-ruler} say to{same}, &apos;Lord, emphatically-not[?] you-sow good sow-effect in to{the your field}[?] So, whence it-is-having tares[?]&apos;
