<verse style="v" number="46" />Moreover, around the ninth hour the Jesus cries-up to{great sound}, saying, &quot;Eli, Eli, lema sabachthani.&quot; The-same is-being &quot;God of{me}, God of{me}, in-which-place what[?] you-leave-in-down/against/leave-behind me[?]&quot;
